0. Product Identity (Platform‑Level Grounding)
Product Name: Orion
Product Type: Enterprise‑grade digital platform supporting medical‑device‑adjacent applications
Classification: Foundational platform (not a clinician‑facing product)
Deployment Model: Hybrid architecture combining:
edge‑resident components (e.g., programmer‑side or locally executed logic)
cloud‑native services hosted in a regulated cloud environment
Primary Role in Ecosystem:
Orion serves as the common digital substrate upon which multiple Medtronic clinical and operational applications are built. It provides shared capabilities that would otherwise need to be re‑implemented separately by each product team.
